snippet.title: Sharknado VR Teaser 30 Seconds (Press Release)
snippet.description: You are stranded in the eye of a tornado...wait, is that a shark? A SHARKNADO! Sharknado: Eye of the Storm is a glorious 360 VR multi level bone shaker.
